About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Pak Champions vs WI Champions | Akmal’s⚡113 Powers 49-Run Win! | Match Highlights | WCL S2 2025
snippet.description:
🏏 Pakistan vs West Indies WCL 2025 Match 11 Highlights! 🏆 Relive the explosive clash at Headingley, Leeds, where Pakistan Champions thrashed West Indies Champions by 49 runs on July 26, 2025, in the World Championship of Legends! 🔥 Pakistan posted a commanding 200/4, powered by Kamran Akmal’s scintillating 113 off 62 balls (13 fours, 5 sixes) and Mohammad Hafeez’s 23 off 18. West Indies faltered at 151/7, with Chadwick Walton’s 42 off 30 and Dwayne Bravo’s 30* off 21, as Rumman Raees’ fiery 3/4 and Sohail Tanvir’s 2/24 sealed the deal. Watch key moments, Akmal’s massive sixes, and post-match reactions from legends like Shahid Afridi and Chris Gayle. Don’t miss Pakistan’s next clash against Australia! 🇵🇰🌴

snippet.description:
From Director James Cameron, watch the trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash.
Experience the film only in theaters December 19.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Britain Dalton, Trinity Bliss, Jack Champion, Bailey Bass and Kate Winslet.

snippet.title: Piya Ghar Aaya - Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan (Asad's Remix)
snippet.description:
All praise to Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan.

I'm excited to finally share the full version. Thanks for waiting so patiently (most of you :p)
I'm starting off my new series called EIGHT x EIGHT with this track, As a part of this series I'll put out a new song every Thursday for the next 8 weeks

I grew up in Pakistan, and I now live in Canada. My family is from Faisalabad. Growing up, my grandfather listened to a lot of qawwali around me as a kid and that influence never left my dna. After years of making music, I finally did something with a track from Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan. I also really enjoyed seeing videos of this track from all over the world, specially from home - thank you for sharing those. 

This remix blew up on TikTok, Instagram etc but more importantly, as you can see in this video, it created a beautiful moment for a group of people and that's what music is all about. Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan's legacy continues to serve moments like this, I'm grateful to have been a vessel. 

Thanks for showing this so much love, lots more music soon

Asad 
-
Download in High Quality: https://asadkhanlife.bandcamp.com/track/piya-ghar-aaya-asads-remix
More music + Socials: https://tr.ee/4Hvf7x

snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMWC at EWC Group Stage Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
GROUP STAGE DAY 1 | JULY 25

2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ka aghaaz ho chuka hai ESPORTS WORLD CUP ke sath, aik dhamakedar Group Stage k pehle din ke sath! Tayyar ho jao ek aur shaandaar summer ke liye jab duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams Riyadh mein takraayengi glory ,legacy , aur $3,000,000 ke inaam ke liye. Aao mil kar dekhein ke kaunsi teams HEAT ko BEAT kar paengi!

Yeh global showdown duniya bhar ki behtareen squads ko ikattha karta hai, jo sab 2025 PMWC jo k EWC ki taraf sy horha hai jeetne ka khwab le kar tayyar hain. Pehle ka aaghaz dhamakedaar matches ke saath hoga, jo agle teen dinon ki sakht muqabla baazi ka manzar zahir kryga.

Is safar ka aaghaz Group Stage se hoga, jahan 24 teams ko 3 groups mein taqseem kiya gya hai jo Grand Finals ke liye apni jagah banane ke liye takrayen gi. Is stage se top 8 teams seedha Grand Finals mein pohnchyn gi, jabke baaqi 16 teams high pressure Survival Stage mein aamna saamna karen gi aakhri 8 slots ke liye. Grand Finals mein 16 behtareen teams ek doosre ke khilaaf glory, pride, aur championship ka taaj pehnny k liye pury josh se takraengi.

🔥 Ap 2025 PMWC jo k EWC mai horha hai miss nahe krna chahyngy.

- Dekho duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams ko Riyadh mein apne waqar ke liye takraate hue!
- Har match mein high-stakes action ka lutf uthao, jo har dafa is dorh ko badal kar rakh dega.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Season 2 | Teaser | Wahaj Ali & Yumna Zaidi | Coming Soon!
snippet.description:
Tere Bin Season 2 | Teaser | Wahaj Ali & Yumna Zaidi | Coming Soon!
#terebinseason2 #terebin #yumnazaidi #wahajali 

Tere Bin Season 2 drama story about revolved around delves into the life of a young woman whose entire world is centered around her parents as she holds an unshakable belief in their guidance and decisions. However her life takes an unexpected turn when she is bound in a marriage forged on a unique and unconventional contract. This contract, meant to maintain boundaries acts as a symbolic wall between her and her husband creating an emotional distance despite their marital bond. As they navigate this complex relationship the story explores themes of trust individuality and the struggle to find connection within imposed limitations. Tere Bin Season 2 Drama Release date on 3rd October 2025.

Tere Bin Season 2 drama is a Pakistani television series produced by Abdullah Kadwani and Asad Qureshi. Tere Bin Season 2 Drama cast Wahaj Ali, Yumna Zaidi, Bushra Ansari in leading roles and many other supporting roles. The Drama Directed by Siraj-ul-Haque and Writer is Nooran Makhdoom under the banner of 7th Sky Entertainment. Tere Bin Season 2 Drama Release date Episode 1 air on 2025 at 8:00 PM. The show’s makers may come up with an altogether new storyline and plot for Tere Bin season 2. The Drama Will be Broadcast on Official Channel on Har Pal Geo TV.  

@WProductions

snippet.description:
CREDITS:
Singer: Muhammad Samie
Poet: Muhammad Samie
Composer: Muhammad Samie
===========================
AUDIO CREW:
Music Production: Jay Ali
Music Direction: Muhammad Samie & Jay Ali
Main Harmonium: Muhammad Samie
Second Harmonium: Jay Ali
Tabla: Irfan Aly
Dholak: Irfan Aly & Kamran Ali
Mandolin & Guitars: Mumtaz Hussain
Chorus Vocals: Ali Hassan, Ali Murtaza & Arslan Ali
Recording: Jay Ali
Mixing & Mastering: Jay Ali
===========================
VIDEO CREW:
Director: Muhammad Samie
Video Concept: Muhammad Samie & Suleman Shah
Cinematographer: Suleman Shah
DOP: Suleman Shah
Gaffer: Usman Rizwan
Art Work: Muhammad Samie
Wardrobe: Muhammad Samie
Lighting Production: Light & Grip Productions
Post-Production: Suleman Shah
Production House: Kul Andar Films

A Presentation by Short Sufi Films
============
LYRICS:
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga
Ali viraasat hai Mustafa ki, Ali hi mash’hood-e-haq rahe ga

Tu wo walad hai jo lam-yalid ke makaan se jalwa-numa hua hai
Tu nashir-e-dawa-e-salooni, tu kya hai? Sab ko guman hua hai
Tu qasim-e-noor-e-Mustafa hai, tu nafs-e-Payghambar-e-Khuda hai
Tu markaz-e-Awliya-e-alam, tu bil-yaqeen fakhr-e-Ambiya hai

Ali mizaaj-e-Muhammadi hai, Ali to asrar-e-haq rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Tu hi Risaalat ki hai khilafat, tu hi wilayat tu hi imamat
Tu kurra-e-arz-e-Kibriya pe Nabi ki hai awaleen shahadat
Tu mehvar-e-ilm-e-do-sara hai, tu kashif-e-maqsad-e-ibadat
Tu hai siraat-e-nijaat-e-insaan, hai qalb-e-momin teri riyasat

Tumhara rahbar tumhain mubarak, hamara rahbar Ali rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Wo badr ho ya mubahila ho, ya phir Muhammad ki wo kisaa ho
Wo chahe Marhab ka samna ho, ya phir wo khandaq ka ma’rka ho
Uhud mein dhaal-e-Payambari ya, buton ka Ka’be se khaatma ho
Ya wo wilayat ki taaj-poshi ba-dast-e-at'haar-e-Mustafa ho

Ali se daman bachane wale, Ali tujhe jaa ba jaa mile ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Nabi ke deen ki ragon mein Haider lahu ki soorat ravaan rahe ga
Ali ka munkir zaleel-o-ruswa azal se tha hashr tak rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali ...

Aao ji Ali Ali wird paka laiyay
Ghaman nu chadd aj khushiyan mana laiyay
Ral ke aakhiye, “Baad Muhammad
Sab ton afzal zikr-e-Ali" Bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Ali de chehre nu takna ibadat
Ali da naan loko japna ibadat
Ki ki mein dassan tenu sifat Ali di
Jane Ali nu Khuda Ya Nabi bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Haider, safdar, sher-e-ghazanfar
Rahbar-e-akbar, mard-e-muzaffar
At'har, azhar, Haq da mazhar
Peeng de andar cheereya azdar
Deen da anbar, Khvaja Qambar
Veer Paighambar, awwal number
Baad Muhammad sab ton bartar
Ikko baan nal puteya Khyber
Ilm samandar, fakhr-e-Sikandar
Mard-e-Qalandar, loon loon andar
Badr ton lay ke Khandak, Khyber
Dushman cheer ke langeya Haider
Tayyab, tahir, banda-parwar
Rooh-e-munawwar, maula, sarwar
Hadi, mahdi, aali-gauhar
Zahra paak da suchha shauhar
Qazi-e-azam, alim-e-alam
Shams-e-wilayat, Noor-e-hidayat
Aashiq Rab da, Paak nasab da
Ghaiz ghazab da, Hunar kasab da
Mahir sab da, Fakhr Arab da
Baap Hassan da, Phol chaman da
Raah adan da, shah zaman da 
Waar Ali da, kair Khuda da
Ishq Ali da, lutf Khuda da
Bol Ali de, hukam Khuda da
Deed Ali di, karam Khuda da

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

#muhammadsamie #shortsufispells #qawwali

snippet.title: Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan 2 - Trailer | Karamjit Anmol | In Cinemas 08 Aug | New Punjabi Movie
snippet.description:
🎬Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan 2 – Official Trailer Releasing in Cinemas this Rakhi – August 8th, 2025

Presented by Ranjiv Singla Productions, this heartfelt sequel to the beloved Punjabi hit "Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan" brings back the powerful story of a father and his four daughters — filled with laughter, love, and life’s beautiful struggles.

👨‍👧‍👧 Celebrate this Rakhi with a story that honors the unbreakable bond between a father and his daughters. Only in theatres from August 8th, 2025.

🎞 Credits
📽 Produced by: Ranjiv Singla
✍ Story & Directed by: Avtar Singh
🖊 Written by: Aman Sidhu
🌟 Starring: Karamjit Anmol, Sukhwinder Raj, Ekta Gulati Khera, Gunveen Manchanda, Avnoor, Mannat Sharma, Pooja Gaba, Raj Dhaliwal, Arry Gill
🎥 Cinematography: Navneet Beohar
✂ Editor: Krishna Rodge
🎵 Music: Amdad Ali, RD Beat
🎤 Singers: Karamjit Anmol, Nachhatar Gill, Rza Heer, Anmol Virk
🎶 Lyrics: Gurbinder Maan, Jaggi Jagsir, Gurri Billing
🎚 Re-Recording Mixing: After Play Studios (Maddy)
🎛 Mixer: Anish Poduval
🎨 Art Director: Balkar Singh (Rustom)
👗 Costume Designer: Asmita Chauhan
🎞 Post Production: Master Prime Studios
📋 Line Production: Vikramjit
📲 Digital Promotion: Creative Benchers
https://www.creativebenchers.com/
🎥 Creative Producer: Inder Bansal
🎬 Executive Producer: Rajinder Kumar Gagahar

🎞 Motion Graphics: Junaid Ansari
